long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This complementary extension from Instaleap helps members find individuals who can help them with jobs, business leads, professional mentoring in the context of the following
-Job they may be looking at on leading job portals
-Company web sites they may be browsing
-Academic institutions they may be looking at on line

The extension shows a recommendation of people who can potentially help, and then the Instaleap user can setup a 1-1 session directly with the recommended members by clicking on the recommendations.

Using this extension, Instaleap members can also set up 1-1 video/audio meetings with other Instaleap members who have specified their professional profiles.


Use of this extension is subject to the Instaleap Terms of Use(https://www.instaleap.me/tos ) and Privacy Policy (https://www.instaleap.me/privacy )
